name: Gather Community Plant #017 - Taccc
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their rendition of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Taccc is a fresh face in the CleanNFT scene currently developing their style and unleashing their mind onto the canvas.

"I feel so happy about how everything is going this last month, I never expected to be well received and know all this beautiful people of the hen and objkt community, it’s really been a pleasure." - Taccc
